                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\"><placeName>Cincin</placeName>,, <date>April 19. 1857</date></p>\n            <p>Rd Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Herewith I enclose 6.00 the amt. of my subscription for the Occident\n                &amp;<lb/> that also of my sons of <placeName>Beloit</placeName>. I send by same\n                post a Packet containing<lb/> particulars of the religious affairs of this place If\n                you find them suitable for yr.<lb/> useful <sic>magizine</sic>. I shall in\n                conjunction with many of our friends here be pleased you<lb/> would publish them. I\n                have endeavored to digest the subject to the best of my ability. I find<lb/> it\n                greatly needs correction, which I trust you will be kind enough to give it.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I have endeavored to follow yr. frequent recommendation as regards\n                moderation<lb/> of style and language &amp; &amp; should any of its sentiments\n                appear to you prompted by<lb/> passion or bad feeling, please to make any alteration\n                or correction that you may<lb/> think best. I would prefer waiting any reasonable\n                time for its insertion rather than<lb/> have the subject continued in succeeding\n                no.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">with best wishes &amp; &amp;</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">I am yr. Respy</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">S. Bruel</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>To the <addressee>Rd I Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Phila</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p>PS. since writing I sent for, but cannot conveniently get a one dollar bill that<lb/>\n                will pass current with you. I will send it on soon by favor. <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                        ><persName role=\"author\">S.B</persName></hi></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3902023w/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
